  <div class="teaser-lg--main">

          <div class="teaser-lg__image">
        
              <a href="/us/blog/side-effects/202306/benzodiazepines-linked-to-long-term-neurological-dysfunction"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn2.psychologytoday.com/assets/styles/manual_crop_1_1_288x288/public/teaser_image/blog_entry/2023-06/shutterstock_1635674116.jpg?h=7619c81e&amp;itok=P8CYhDZ4" width="288" height="288" alt="" title="shaneinsweden / Shutterstock" />

</a>

      
      </div>
    
    <div class="teaser-lg__details">
      
                        <div class="h2 teaser-lg__title">
            <a href="/us/blog/side-effects/202306/benzodiazepines-linked-to-long-term-neurological-dysfunction" rel="bookmark">Benzodiazepines Linked to Long-Term Neurological Dysfunction</a>
          </div>
              
      
              <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--desktop">
            A large survey of benzodiazepine withdrawal found that almost half of respondents experienced drug-related symptoms more than a year later.
      </p>
          </div>

  </div>

      <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--mobile">
            A large survey of benzodiazepine withdrawal found that almost half of respondents experienced drug-related symptoms more than a year later.
      </p>
  </article>
</div>

    
    
